Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:11.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You gotta really flap 'em hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:18.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Maybe not quite that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:25.99,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Lookin' good up there, Princess Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:28.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Applejack, you know you don't have to call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:33.29,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why do you protest so? You've already given up wearing your crown all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:36.07,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The least you can do is embrace your new title.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:40.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If other ponies want to address me that way, I suppose it's fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:43.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,not my friends. It just doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:47.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And neither does all this flying business.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:49.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Summer Sun Celebration is only two days away,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:52.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and I'm never gonna be ready to perform my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:54.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Not if you spend all your time down here, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Now get up there and show everypony the big finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:31.17,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wow! That was a big finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:18.95,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You look amazing, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They've really captured your regality!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:23.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:25.25,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be so modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:28.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It's everypony's dream to someday wear a crown and have their
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:31.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,coronation ceremony preserved in stained glass for all to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:34.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's everypony's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Most of my dreams are about frosting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:42.03,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We'd better get going. We don't wanna miss our train.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.24,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.30,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Don't know about y'all, but I've still got bushels to do to get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The official celebration may be here in Canterlot,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:52.86,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but hoo-ee has the Mayor put us in charge of one heck of a party back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:57.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Aw, don't look like that, sugarcube.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:03:01.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You get to be right there with the other Princesses when Celestia raises the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:03.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I'm honored. Really, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:07.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's just that the Summer Sun Celebration was what first brought us all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:12.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It just doesn't feel right not getting to spend such a special day with my Ponyville friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:15.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel right to us either, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:19.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,If the Mayor wasn't so desperate for our assistance, we'd most certainly stay here in Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:23.75,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And, of course, we do understand that your royal duties must come first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:26.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The Summer Sun Celebration may have brought us together,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:30.24,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but it's something much bigger that will always keep us connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:32.26,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Exhibit A:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:35.53,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,the six of us are united by the Elements of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:38.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,No amount of royal duties is gonna change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:40.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Right, everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.22,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Right, Pinkie Pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:47.14,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Creamy-creamy frosting…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.11,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You should take that as a "yes"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:58.95,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We're gonna write to you and give you so many details that it'll be like you're in Ponyville with us! Right, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:03.35,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Cross my heart and hope to fly,\Nstick a cupcake in my eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:06.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And you will be with us right after the celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:10.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We already have an appointment on the books to discuss the royal updates to your loft decor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:14.15,Somepony,,0,0,0,,All aboard for Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:28.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't help it, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:32.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,They've only been gone for a minute, and I already feel like I'm missing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:34.39,Somepony,,0,0,0,,For the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,Dear Twilight, you're not missing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.34,Spike,,0,0,0,,Your friend, Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.07,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,THAT'S MEEE!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:45.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I just know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:50.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,Check, check, check, check,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:51.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,and… check!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:54.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,Huh, would you know, we're way ahead of schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:57.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,I credit your extremely competent assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:04:59.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:02.84,Spike,,0,0,0,,The Celebration isn't until the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:06.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,We could still fit in a quick trip to Ponyville and be back in plenty of time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:09.22,Spike,,0,0,0,,to finish off these last few things before the main event!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:11.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That would be nice, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But what if something else cаme up when we are gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:17.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What if we were delayed getting back and I wasn't able to finish everything on that list?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:22.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What if we lost the list on the way to Ponyville and then couldn't remember which things we'd done and which things we hadn't done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And then spent so much time trying to figure out what we hadn't done and what we had done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:30.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And we ruined the entire Celebration by not doing the one really important thing we were supposed to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:33.27,Spike,,0,0,0,,So that's a "no", then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is the first royal duty Princess Celestia has given me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't risk letting her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.36,Celestia,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:49.75,Celestia,,0,0,0,,No need for that now, Princess Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:51.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.32,Celestia,,0,0,0,,No need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:06:01.67,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I must admit that it's wonderful to actually be looking forward to the Summer Sun Celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:07.62,Celestia,,0,0,0,,For my subjects, it has always been a celebration of my defeat of Nightmare Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:09.15,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But for me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:13.36,Celestia,,0,0,0,,it was just a terrible reminder that I had to banish my own sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I guess, I never really thought about it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:23.32,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But now it has become a wonderful reminder of her transformation back into Princess Luna
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.99,Celestia,,0,0,0,,and our happy reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:29.04,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I am so pleased that you'll be playing a role in the festivities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:33.31,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I know it must have been difficult to see your friends return to Ponyville without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:37.82,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You may no longer be my student, Princess Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:41.40,Celestia,,0,0,0,,but I hope you know I will always be here if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:44.85,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Just as I hope you'll always be here when I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.31,Spike,,0,0,0,,I think, this guy needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:51.65,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Message for Princess Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:58.02,Celestia,,0,0,0,,A letter from Ponyville, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:00.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Nevermind. It's not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike, where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.99,Spike,,0,0,0,,About to call it a night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:07.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We should probably get over the checklist one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:09.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,I knew you were gonna to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.65,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I'll leave you to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:34.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,Check-check-check-check-check-check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:37.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But it could be morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:45.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's just it, I can't tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:50.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,That is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike. We've got to find out, what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.87,Somepony,,0,0,0,,What do you think it means?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.98,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight will know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm-I'm sure it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:08.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's certainly a logical ex–
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:11.02,Guard,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, you must come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:17.22,Guard,,0,0,0,,It's Princess Luna and Princess Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:18.90,Guard,,0,0,0,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:27.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I don't understand. Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.20,Guard,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:31.85,Guard,,0,0,0,,It seems like Princess Luna and Princess Celestia have simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.37,Guard,,0,0,0,,vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:34.63,Spike,,0,0,0,,Vanished?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.72,Guard,,0,0,0,,This is why we have come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:39.95,Guard,,0,0,0,,We await your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:41.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My command?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.71,Guard,,0,0,0,,We're officers of the Royal Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.75,Guard,,0,0,0,,We take our orders from royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.66,Guard,,0,0,0,,With Princess Luna and Princess Celestia gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:52.70,Guard,,0,0,0,,and Princess Cadance overseeing the Crystal Empire now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:55.56,Guard,,0,0,0,,that means we take our orders from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:58.01,Guard,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:01.67,Guard,,0,0,0,,There's no time to waste. We need to know what you want us to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:07.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I want you to continue the search for Princess Luna and Princess Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:10.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We have to find them before ponies start to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:13.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There must be some clue that can tell us what's happened to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:16.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If you find something, anything, let me know immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,Way to take charge, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:24.36,Guard,,0,0,0,,Your highness, news from Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.75,Guard,,0,0,0,,The Everfree Forest appears to be…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.63,Guard,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.32,Guard,,0,0,0,,Invading!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:34.52,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.25,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:37.93,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:47.07,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,My goodness, what is it that has caused you all such distress?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:53.58,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is, I'm sure it's nothing you need to really worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:02.19,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,No, you're right. You should be worried. Very very worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:11.08,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come on y'all! Put your backs into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:17.47,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:19.02,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:20.43,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:21.87,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:23.39,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:24.76,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Dangabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:32.97,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We've never seen this kind of trouble with weeds before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:37.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, I've never seen these kinds of weeds at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:38.68,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Have y'all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:40.19,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:43.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Where the heck are these thing coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:47.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And what in tarnation is going on with the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:50.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh no you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:53.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,This is Ponyville territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:57.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And we aren't due for rain until after the Summer Sun Celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:11:01.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You Everfree clouds just head back to where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.94,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Gonna make me do this the hard way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:23.58,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Something's strange about the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:45.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What in the name of calming chamomile is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:50.70,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Opalescence, darling, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.43,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I promise, I'm not doing this on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.07,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me. I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:05.08,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.17,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Is this some sort of prank you and your little crusader friends are pulling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.25,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I find very little humor in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:14.39,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Rarity, you have to help me! I think something's wrong with my horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:29.74,Spike,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:33.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Everfree Forest is… invading?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:37.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Whatever is going on, I'm sure we're going to need our friends and the Elements of Harmony to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I just hope we haven't miss the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:42.63,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hey Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:45.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,There's another way for us to get to Ponyville, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:46.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:50.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,You can fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:53.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.69,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Something very strange is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:18.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I for one would appreciate an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:23.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,, All I know is the sky's split in two, and these clouds moving in sure aren't from around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:26.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And neither are all these crazy plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:29.97,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,They're coming from the Everfree Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:34.20,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And try as we might, us earth ponies can't do anything to get rid of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:37.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Don't suppose you know any magic that might stop 'em from spreading?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:42.17,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Alas, this whole raging forest situation seems to have left my horn on the fritz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.33,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We have to figure out something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.92,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't know how much more of it Ponyville can take.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.03,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't know how much more of it I can take.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:52.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The forest is expanding, y'all,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:57.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,and judging by how fast it's moving, It doesn't seem content just taking over Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:01.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I reckon before long it'll cover half of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:25.12,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to wish we'd taken the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:29.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike. We need to get Elements of Harmony and find the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.24,Spike,,0,0,0,,Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:45.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:48.79,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I hope you know we wouldn't normally go through your books without your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:54.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,Sweet ground. Sweet, sweet, wonderful ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:57.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Ok, I get it, I need to work on my flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:14:59.40,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you've noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:03.19,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,but the Everfree Forest is just a teeny-tiny bit out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.78,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Guess it turned out you were missing something in Ponyville after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:15.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But perhaps you already know what's causing all of this calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:18.81,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Has Princess Celestia sent you to dispell it post-haste?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:21.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:23.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You see, Princess Celestia is…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:27.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, she and Princess Luna are both…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:29.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,They're missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:32.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know who has taken them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:35.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but I've got a hunch we're going to need the Elements of Harmony to get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:39.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Just like old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.60,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I told you we'd always be connected by the Elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:52.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now we just got to figure out who to aim these bad boys at
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:56.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,so we can get Celestia and Luna back and keep the rest of Equestria from becoming plant food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:58.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:02.55,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I haven't found squat in any of the books I've been looking through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.01,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oopsies, missed a spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Half-day, half night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:13.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Strange weather patterns. Out-of-control plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:17.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think I'm starting to get a pretty good idea of who we're up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:47.10,Discord,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Winter wrap up, winter wrap up… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:53.82,Discord,,0,0,0,,Now, Twilight, you know Princess Celestia said that you were to give me a heads-up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:58.02,Discord,,0,0,0,,before you summon me with that little spell she gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:17:03.77,Discord,,0,0,0,,In case you haven't noticed, I was in the middle of a particularly invigorating shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Release Princess Celestia and Princess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:10.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And stop the Everfree Forest from invading!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:15.16,Discord,,0,0,0,,Whay, whatever are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Dont's you dare play dumb with us, Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.91,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We know you are the one behind all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:26.28,Discord,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong, I absolutely love what you've done with the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:29.57,Discord,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't possibly take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:31.88,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm reformed, don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:37.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! This has got your cloven hoofprints all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:41.62,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, have you know that I only have one cloven hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.85,Discord,,0,0,0,,Such accusations!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.05,Discord,,0,0,0,,And here I thought we were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:51.68,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Cut the act, buster! We're onto you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:56.78,Discord,,0,0,0,, Ladies, ladies! I'm innocent! Would I lie to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:57.86,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:59.51,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:03.30,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well then, it seems we've reached an impasse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:06.12,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm telling the truth, but you think I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:10.94,Discord,,0,0,0,,What do friends like us do in situations like this, Princess Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:15.71,Discord,,0,0,0,,Congrats, by the way, on the promotion, you totally deserve it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:18.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I say, we blast him back to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:19.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Hear, hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:26.68,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We can't do that. What if he really is telling the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:33.11,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, finally, some pony to give me the benefit of the doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:37.05,Discord,,0,0,0,,The rest of you could learn a lot about friendship from my dear friend Shutterfly here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.24,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Um, it's Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.58,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:43.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If you're not responsible, then help us figure out who is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:47.75,Discord,,0,0,0,,I suppose I could, but after all the hoof-pointing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:53.39,Discord,,0,0,0,,and besmearching my good name I just don't know if I'm up to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:19:00.15,Discord,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask your zebra friend if she knows anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:03.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Zecora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:09.59,Zecora,,0,0,0,,From my home I had to flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:13.25,Zecora,,0,0,0,,The forest has grown too wild even for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Any idea why all this is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:18.62,Zecora,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid it is a mystery as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:23.65,Zecora,,0,0,0,,but I may have something that if combined with a spell…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.75,Zecora,,0,0,0,,I do not dare to use it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:32.76,Zecora,,0,0,0,,The result would be tragic. \N It only responds to alicorn magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:39.98,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight, you can turn the potion from purple to white.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:46.28,Zecora,,0,0,0,,After a sip you may see why the sky is day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem to be worki~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:18.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.00,Luna,,0,0,0,,Not... another step!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:24.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:29.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. Where are we? Why did you and Celestia disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:36.40,Luna,,0,0,0,,Did you really expect me to sit idly by while they all basked in your precious light?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:38.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Precious light?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:41.40,Luna,,0,0,0,,There can only be one princess in Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.18,Luna,,0,0,0,,And that princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.68,Luna,,0,0,0,,WILL BE ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:31.83,Somepony,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:34.43,Somepony,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVYI` PONETC
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:36.58,Somepony,,0,0,0,,anon 2 anon \Nsunnysubs.com
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:38.78,Somepony,,0,0,0,,That time will come one day\NYou'll see when we can all be friends
